Txt_Talk_DreamTower_MAIN_0_SCENE_0010_01.Text: *: Oh, hello there! Came here to take the trial, did you? Me too!
*: Crikey, though<--->it's a lot further down than it looks from the bottom, eh?
*: Think I might have to make my excuses and slope off home with my tail between my legs! Heh heh!

Txt_Talk_DreamTower_MAIN_0_ACTOR_0110_01.Text: *: I tell you what<--->if they'd told me how scary it was gonna be, I'd've stayed at home where I belong!

Txt_Talk_DreamTower_MAIN_0_ACTOR_0210_01.Text: *: Eh? Whassat? Jumping off too, are you? Well, wait your blooming turn!

Txt_Talk_DreamTower_MAIN_0_ACTOR_0210_02.Text:
*: Last one down's a rotten egg!
WAHEEEEEEY!!!

Txt_Talk_DreamTower_MAIN_0_ACTOR_0310_01.Text: *: Yay! Finally, my chance to show everyone how brave I really am!
*: If I can do this, I can do anything!

Txt_Talk_DreamTower_MAIN_0_ACTOR_0310_02.Text: *: Ha! What a great big wimp!
*: I'll show you lot how it's done!

Txt_Talk_DreamTower_MAIN_0_ACTOR_0410_01.Text:
*: Eek! Don'tlookdowndon'tlookdown!
Eurgh, I think I'm going to be sick!
*: ...What am I doing!? What's the point in trying to impress people if you end up dying in the process? It's stupid, right?

*: E-Exactly! I knew you'd agree with me!
Right then, let's just step away from the edge and get on with our lives, shall we?

*: N-No...? So...you think I should jump...?
Ulp... Alright then... Here goes...

*: Aieee!
It's no good! I can't do it!
My legs won't let me!

Txt_Talk_DreamTower_MAIN_0_ACTOR_0410_02.Text: *: Sorry. I just don't have it in me...
*: Er... Can I please be excused?

Txt_Talk_DreamTower_MAIN_0_ACTOR_0510_01.Text: *: Well, don't just stand there! Make your mind up, will you? To jump, or not to jump, that's the question!

Txt_Talk_DreamTower_MAIN_0_ACTOR_0510_02.Text: *: Well? What's it to be? I'm not going to twist your arm, you know.
*: Just remember that sometimes discretion is the better part of valour. It's entirely up to you, though...

Txt_Talk_DreamTower_MAIN_0_ACTOR_0610_01.Text: *: Itchin' to jump so badly that you can't wait yer turn, eh? Well...feel free to JUMP THE QUEUE! Heh heh heh!

Txt_Talk_DreamTower_MAIN_0_ACTOR_0610_02.Text:
*: Ye're up! I bet ye're JUMPIN' FOR JOY, intcha?
Heh heh heh!

Txt_Talk_DreamTower_MAIN_0_ACTOR_0710_01.Text:
*: Hm?
You want to go back down, do you?

*: Fair enough.
There's no shame in that.
*: Just make your way down the stairs over there.

*: Blimey. Fair enough.
On you go, then.
